Package fr.iutvalence.projets4.clientsnmp.MIB

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MIBComposite
    A MIBComposite is a composite of the MIB tree (a component who have composites "a node" or an element who have a behavior "a leaf") We can get its sub-composites and set a new sub-composite to this element.
    MIBElement<T>
    A MIBElement is a leaf of the MIB tree who have a behavior
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HwCpuUsage
    Class who gives us the device's CPU Usage PROBLEM : It gives an approximate value Created by Thundermist on 09/01/17.
    HwDiskUsage
    Class who gives us the device's Disk Usage PROBLEM : It gives only the internal disk usage (it don't work with SD cards memories) Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
    HwMemoryUsage
    Class who gives us the device's Memory Usage Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
    HwSensorActivity
    Class who gives us the device's Temperature Created by Thundermist on 09/01/17.
    MIBComponent
    A MIBComponent is a node of the MIB tree.
    MIBDictionary
    Represents the dictionary of the MIB It creates and fill the MIB It allows the access to a MIBElement.
    SrvcForegroundTMM
    Class who checks if there is a TMM app in the foreground PROBLEM : This method is deprecated in Android Lollipop (API 21) for security reasons and not replaced Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
    SrvcMustBeOpen
    Class who checks if every TMM services are open PROBLEM : This method is deprecated in Android Nougat (API 24) for security reasons and not replaced LIBRARY USED : https://github.com/jaredrummler/AndroidProcesses Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
    SysAndroidVersion
    Class who gives us the device's android version Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
    SysDescr
    Class who gives us the device's description Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
    SysUpTime
    Class who gives us the device uptime Created by ethis on 09/01/17.
